<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-1a' );" name="009-1a" class="pb">[009-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　周易章句證異卷九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:223'>　　　　　　　　　　　内閣中書翟均廉撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:229'>文言𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='229:265'>　鄭𤣥文言與説序雜合為一卷<span class='krp-note'>本崇文總目合案淳/于後謂康成  彖象</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='265:307'>　<span class='krp-note'>于經不言合文言于經也朱震吕祖謙嘗從/其説林票亦以文言與説序雜合為一卷</span>王弼附</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='307:348'>　文言于乾坤二卦<span class='krp-note'>小象之後張陸徳明孔頴達李鼎/祚及蘇軾  子程子從之  宋子</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='348:397'>　<span class='krp-note'>夏𫝊朱震李衡鄭汝諧項安世王宗𫝊趙彦肅王申/子李簡董楷同  周燔文言亦附小象後惟大象列</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='397:423'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-1b' );" name="009-1b" class="pb">[009-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='423:473'>　<span class='krp-note'>卦詞前過董真卿文言𫝊附小象後惟大象列彖𫝊/前  李  方逢辰文言釋彖處附彖後大象前釋爻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='473:513'>　<span class='krp-note'>處附小象後无趙汝楳文言釋彖/處附爻辭前  文言𫝊曰等字</span>胡旦復出文言别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='513:557'>　為一篇<span class='krp-note'>析乾文言為第四坤文言為第五在小象後/上繫前  胡瑗合乾坤文言次第五在小象</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='557:606'>　<span class='krp-note'>後上繫前為程迥次同惟象分上下/惟以小象  繫詞下以繫詞為説卦</span>　<span class='krp-note'>吳仁傑亦同/邵子晁説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='606:655'>　<span class='krp-note'>次第四在象後繫詞前謙吕大防連二經次第九在/小繫後説卦前  吕祖  次第七在繫詞下𫝊後説</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='655:704'>　<span class='krp-note'>卦𫝊前朱子從之/良輔梁寅諸人同</span>　<span class='krp-note'>税與權吳澄胡炳文胡一桂熊/俞琰次第九在大象後説卦前</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='704:736'>　　王洙卦辭文言俱不附經<span class='krp-note'>卦詞為一篇次第/一文言次第五</span>　蔡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='736:769'>　淵彖𫝊仍附經中出文言列繫辭後<span class='krp-note'>云古本文言下/有𫝊字今脱</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='769:795'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-2a' );" name="009-2a" class="pb">[009-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='795:819'>　<span class='krp-note'>案吕祖謙朱子税與權/吳澄諸儒俱有𫝊字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='819:835'>　鄭厚无文言<span class='krp-note'>云後人/所作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='835:858'>元者善之長也亨者嘉之會也利者義之和也貞者事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='858:863'>之幹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='863:899'>　王弼加文言曰三字于首<span class='krp-note'>孔穎達李鼎祚蘇軾張謙/子程子諸儒同  吕祖</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='899:946'>　<span class='krp-note'>朱子復析文言為一篇省文言曰三字因毛竒齡曰/宋儒偽造古易謂王氏附文言于乾坤  加文言字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='946:984'>　<span class='krp-note'>以别之不知文言/章次皆舊所定</span>趙汝楳无文言曰三字<span class='krp-note'>直接/彖𫝊</span>　左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='984:1008'>　𫝊穆姜引作元體之長也亨嘉之會也利義之和也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='1008:1034'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-2b' );" name="009-2b" class="pb">[009-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1034:1042'>　貞事之幹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1042:1065'>君子體仁足以長人嘉會足以合禮利物足以和義貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1065:1072'>固足以幹事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1072:1096'>　左𫝊穆姜引無君子字　體仁京房荀爽董遇作體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1096:1124'>　信<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡/云誤</span>　嘉會穆姜引作嘉體　利物孟喜京房</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1124:1134'>　荀爽陸績作利之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1134:1150'>君子行此四徳者故曰乾元亨利貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1150:1173'>初九曰潛龍勿用何謂也子曰龍徳而隱者也不易乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1173:1199'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-3a' );" name="009-3a" class="pb">[009-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1199:1222'>世不成乎名遯世无悶不見是而无悶樂則行之憂則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1222:1235'>違之確乎其不可拔潛龍也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1235:1268'>　吳澄省子曰字<span class='krp-note'>云子曰後人所/加  後五節同</span>　陸徳明李鼎祚作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1268:1307'>　不易世不成名<span class='krp-note'>廉案唐以後本不/易乎世不易乎名</span>　遯惠棟作<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0735' title='KR0735' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0735.png'/></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1307:1315'>　確惠棟作寉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1315:1338'>九二曰見龍在田利見大人何謂也子曰龍徳而正中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1338:1361'>者也庸言之信庸行之謹閑邪存其誠善世而不伐徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1361:1379'>博而化易曰見龍在田利見大人君徳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1379:1405'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-3b' );" name="009-3b" class="pb">[009-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1405:1436'>　吳澄无易曰見龍在田三句<span class='krp-note'>云十三字葢/下文重出</span>　鄭𤣥作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1436:1452'>　閑邪以存其誠<span class='krp-note'>本晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1452:1475'>九三曰君子終日乾乾夕惕若厲无咎何謂也子曰君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1475:1498'>子進徳脩業忠信所以進徳也脩辭立其誠所以居業</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1498:1521'>也知至至之可與㡬也知終終之可與存義也是故居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1521:1544'>上位而不驕在下位而不憂故乾乾因其時而惕雖危</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1544:1549'>无咎矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1549:1560'>　惠棟亦作夕惕若夤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1560:1586'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-4a' );" name="009-4a" class="pb">[009-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1586:1609'>九四曰或躍在淵无咎何謂也子曰上下无常非為邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1609:1632'>也進退无恆非離羣也君子進徳脩業欲及時也故无</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1632:1635'>咎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1635:1667'>　鄭𤣥作君子進徳脩業及時无欲字也字<span class='krp-note'>本晁説之/  惠棟同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1667:1690'>九五曰飛龍在天利見大人何謂也子曰同聲相應同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1690:1713'>氣相求水流濕火就燥雲從龍風從虎聖人作而萬物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1713:1734'>覩本乎天者親上本乎地者親下則各從其類也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1734:1742'>　作馬融作起</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1742:1768'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-4b' );" name="009-4b" class="pb">[009-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1768:1791'>上九曰亢龍有悔何謂也子曰貴而无位高而无民賢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1791:1807'>人在下位而无輔是以動而有悔也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1807:1830'>　熊朋來湛若水呉澄毛竒齡俱以繫辭亢龍有悔節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1830:1839'>　為即文言脱誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1839:1847'>潛龍勿用下也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1847:1856'>見龍在田時舍也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1856:1865'>終日乾乾行事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1865:1874'>或躍在淵自試也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1874:1900'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-5a' );" name="009-5a" class="pb">[009-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1900:1909'>飛龍在天上治也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1909:1919'>亢龍有悔窮之災也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1919:1937'>　鄭𤣥作窮志災也<span class='krp-note'>本晁/説之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1937:1947'>乾元用九天下治也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1947:1957'>潛龍勿用陽氣潛藏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1957:1967'>見龍在田天下文明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1967:1977'>終日乾乾與時偕行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1977:1987'>或躍在淵乾道乃革</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1987:2013'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-5b' );" name="009-5b" class="pb">[009-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2013:2024'>飛龍在天乃位乎天徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2024:2034'>亢龍有悔與時偕極</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2034:2044'>乾元用九乃見天則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2044:2054'>乾元者始而亨者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2054:2062'>利貞者性情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2062:2088'>　鄭𤣥作情性也<span class='krp-note'>本晁説之朱震/  呉澄惠棟同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2088:2106'>乾始能以美利利天下不言所利大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2106:2142'>　鄭𤣥作乾始而以美利利天下<span class='krp-note'>本晁説之案李鼎祚/惠棟同廉  而古能</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2142:2168'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-6a' );" name="009-6a" class="pb">[009-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2168:2179'>　<span class='krp-note'>字説見/上經</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2179:2193'>大哉乾乎剛健中正純粹精也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2193:2230'>　粹惠棟作晬<span class='krp-note'>荀子非相曰而能容雜劉淵林吳/都賦注云不雜曰晬雜者晬之反</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2230:2241'>六爻𤼵揮旁通情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2241:2259'>　揮陸徳明本亦作輝<span class='krp-note'>義取/光輝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2259:2277'>時乘六龍以御天也雲行雨施天下平也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2277:2300'>君子以成徳為行日可見之行也潛之為言也隱而未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2300:2314'>見行而未成是以君子弗用也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2314:2340'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-6b' );" name="009-6b" class="pb">[009-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2340:2363'>君子學以聚之問以辨之寛以居之仁以行之易曰見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2363:2375'>龍在田利見大人君徳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2375:2398'>九三重剛而不中上不在天下不在田故乾乾因其時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2398:2407'>而惕雖危无咎矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2407:2430'>九四重剛而不中上不在天下不在田中不在人故或</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2430:2442'>之或之者疑之也故无咎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2442:2476'>　朱子曰九四非重剛重字疑衍<span class='krp-note'>陸時位曰虞仲翔云/以乾接乾故重剛李</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2476:2522'>　<span class='krp-note'>鼎祚重卦自此二爻始故云朱義謂陽爻陽位為重/剛而以九四重剛為衍文失象㫖矣廉按諸儒皆作</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2522:2548'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-7a' );" name="009-7a" class="pb">[009-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2548:2580'>　<span class='krp-note'>重剛胡炳文本義通釋梁寅易叅/義熊良輔本義集成亦不從本義</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2580:2603'>夫大人者與天地合其徳與日月合其明與四時合其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2603:2626'>序與鬼神合其吉凶先天而天弗違後天而奉天時天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2626:2641'>且勿違而况于人乎况于鬼神乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2641:2655'>　而况于人乎李鼎祚无而字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2655:2678'>亢之為言也知進而不知退知存而不知亡知得而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2678:2682'>知喪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2682:2705'>其唯聖人乎知進退存亡而不失其正者其唯聖人乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2705:2731'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-7b' );" name="009-7b" class="pb">[009-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2731:2765'>　首句王肅作愚人後結始作聖人<span class='krp-note'>俞琰曰王肅謬矣/  胡瑗以首句為</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2765:2779'>　<span class='krp-note'>羡/文</span>呉澄刪去首句</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2779:2793'>坤至柔而動也剛至静而徳方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2793:2811'>　王弼以下附坤卦者皆有文言曰三字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2811:2819'>後得主而有常</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2819:2858'>　程子曰主下脱利字<span class='krp-note'>朱子從之文鄭汝諧王申子胡/一桂胡炳  董楷梁寅陸仁錫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2858:2907'>　<span class='krp-note'>林希元程竹山同𫝊余苞曰程朱以主利句遂以文/言為闕文然觀彖  意未見其為闕文也  陸時位</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2907:2942'>　<span class='krp-note'>曰朱子考亭云當有利字武斷之過説/毛竒齡曰程朱増此字曲全主利之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2942:2968'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-8a' );" name="009-8a" class="pb">[009-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2968:2976'>含萬物而化光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2976:2988'>坤道其順乎承天而時行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2988:3018'>　張元冲𫝊載晉王易本作順承乎天而時行<span class='krp-note'>毛竒齡/曰乃與</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3018:3032'>　<span class='krp-note'>順承天合/較似有理</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3032:3055'>積善之家必有餘慶積不善之家必有餘殃臣弑其君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3055:3078'>子弑其殳非一朝一夕之故其所由來者漸矣由辨之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3078:3095'>不早辨也易曰履霜堅氷至蓋言順也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3095:3125'>　辨荀爽作變<span class='krp-note'>晁説之云辨/古文變字</span>　順楊萬里曰當作馴朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3125:3151'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-8b' );" name="009-8b" class="pb">[009-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3151:3185'>　子曰古字順慎通用此當作慎<span class='krp-note'>胡氏炳文曰諸家釋/順字謂善與不善皆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3185:3232'>　<span class='krp-note'>由順而後釋本義作慎言當辨之于微也讀作順字/不若慎字有下工夫處  呉澄改作慎廉案荀爽及</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3232:3250'>　<span class='krp-note'>程子諸儒皆作/順訓與慎義異</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3250:3273'>直其正也方其義也君子敬以直内義以方外敬義立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3273:3294'>而徳不孤直方大不習无不利則不疑其所行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3294:3317'>　俞琰云或曰禮記云直其政政乃敬之訛敬訛為政</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3317:3358'>　政又轉而為正<span class='krp-note'>案惠棟云正當為敬字之誤此毛竒/齡云案古文變換處多不拘  不必</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3358:3385'>　<span class='krp-note'>穿/鑿</span>俞琰曰劉元城嘗改敬以直内為正以直内不知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3385:3411'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-9a' );" name="009-9a" class="pb">[009-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3411:3434'>　言敬則正在其中　張璠曰直方大上有象曰二字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3434:3443'>　<span class='krp-note'>惠棟/同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3443:3466'>隂雖有美含之以從王事弗敢成也地道也妻道也臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3466:3479'>道也地道无成而代有終也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3479:3518'>　宋衷作含之以從王事<span class='krp-note'>句朱震同從張振淵曰當以/  含之以  王事為句若依</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3518:3566'>　<span class='krp-note'>胡雲峯以隂雖有美含之為句則以從王事上反費/轉摺  查慎行同  項安世曰以含之連下文讀者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3566:3583'>　<span class='krp-note'>非亷案諸儒俱/以含之絶句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3583:3606'>天地變化草木蕃天地閉賢人隱易曰括囊无咎无譽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3606:3632'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-9b' );" name="009-9b" class="pb">[009-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3632:3638'>蓋言謹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3638:3646'>君子黄中通理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3646:3682'>　王申子以君子黄中<span class='krp-note'>句云通理二字即小象文在/  中之意非連黄中為句</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3682:3688'>正位居體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3688:3708'>美在其中而暢於四支𤼵於事業美之至也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3708:3731'>隂疑於陽必戰為其嫌於无陽也故稱龍焉猶未離其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3731:3755'>類也故稱血焉夫𤣥黄者天地之雜也天𤣥而地黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3755:3789'>　荀爽虞翻姚信蜀才作隂凝于陽<span class='krp-note'>晁説之曰疑古文/凝字  惠棟從凝</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3789:3816'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0162', 'WYG', '009-10a' );" name="009-10a" class="pb">[009-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3816:3848'>　　嫌荀爽虞翻陸績九家易董遇作兼<span class='krp-note'>李氏鼎祚同/  惠棟作兼</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3848:3895'>　<span class='krp-note'>云俗/作嫌</span>鄭𤣥作慊<span class='krp-note'>讀如羣公溓之溓古書篆作立心與/水相近讀者失之故作溓溓雜也廉</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3895:3934'>　<span class='krp-note'>案釋文引鄭作謙此本詩采薇正/義  毛竒齡曰兼慊溓皆非正義</span>　雜惠棟作襍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3934:3957'>　熊朋來吳澄湛若水毛竒齡以繫辭中十六卦爻辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3957:3974'>　十八節皆屬文言<span class='krp-note'>説詳/繫辭</span></span><br/>
